{"id":31076,"title":"[Prevention and vaccination against hepatitis].","abstract":"Vaccines against hepatitisA and B are today available and effective. The prevention of hepatitis is thereby based on the reduction of the risk of infection, notably among drug users. France is experimenting with a supervised drug consumption room. For professionals, information, training and physical means of protection are essential to avoid contamination. The operating theatre is an example of a treatment area which is particularly concerned.","date":"2014-01-13","categories":"Chemically-Induced Disorders","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24409612","annotations":[{"name":"Vaccine","weight":0.781843,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vaccine"},{"name":"Infection","weight":0.756683,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Infection"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.751095,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Vaccination","weight":0.728698,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vaccination"},{"name":"Drug","weight":0.713367,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Drug"},{"name":"Hepatitis","weight":0.710976,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hepatitis"},{"name":"Preventive medicine","weight":0.692772,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Preventive_medicine"},{"name":"France","weight":0.645301,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/France"},{"name":"Violence","weight":0.577669,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Violence"},{"name":"Tuberculosis","weight":0.485032,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tuberculosis"},{"name":"Risk","weight":0.438221,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Risk"},{"name":"Operating theater","weight":0.316587,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Operating_theater"},{"name":"Substance abuse","weight":0.263112,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Substance_abuse"}